{"tid":668794,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"韋舒亞大控訴：我應該入選！","createTime":"2018-05-18T02:36:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T12:36:10.000Z","uid":46892,"like":12,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"30a37971ade967133a5acefa3cf97b15603497ba","tid":668794,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T02:36:13.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=0lMTb%2Be1X1udiJY8OEQYvMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=6f1d643b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】失落英格蘭決賽周23人大軍的韋舒亞，透過社交網絡作出控訴，直言自覺應該獲召用並為英軍帶來影響力。<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴中場韋舒亞（Jack Wilshere）在社交網絡盡吐心中情，言詞間顯得忿忿不平：「不消說我很自然為落選英格蘭的世界盃大軍感失望，我整季都感覺有狀態、銳利及強壯，深信自己該入選大軍！只要機會來到，我本可帶來影響力。」<br />\n<br />\n不過他還是為三獅送上祝福：「不過，我得尊重領隊的決定，祝福全隊在賽事表現出色，我永遠是英格蘭球迷，與國家其他人一起支持球員。」<br />\n<br />\n早於周三，韋舒亞已在社交網上載一張令人忍俊不禁的照片，那是他和赫特以往入選英軍時的相片，相中兩人一起在游泳池，赫特以食指指向鬱悶的韋舒亞，他的留言是：「不要聽他們的，Jack！我們都是優秀足球員！」這個留言語帶相關，實在幽默得很。"},{"pid":"637ba1db56422efca01f1a9249034de1804dad4d","tid":668794,"uid":19552,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T02:38:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/BsicB6FIEAAdq_t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FBsicB6FIEAAdq_t.jpg&h=fafc414d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a9e99d110ad8ee2d3e12afecd28f49e7d77d7c2","tid":668794,"uid":70846,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T02:38:37.000Z","msg":"黑碧有得入太子無，我係佢都覺得唔抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66914ddcc5d8a843a2971262c5d78e99c81e4e64","tid":668794,"uid":46892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T02:39:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/BsicB6FIEAAdq_t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FBsicB6FIEAAdq_t.jpg&h=fafc414d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"